Watch yourself down here!\nRubble! Ice! Gross water! Danger!\pProve to me you're prepared for\nperil, with a Pok\emon battle!

#org @gText_IcedPath_CamperRoss_Lose
You're clear to go, friend!

#org @gText_IcedPath_CamperRoss_After
Saffron's trains are out of service.\pBut, when they were running, they'd\nshake this whole place up!

