My Kecleon is really taking to\nthis crazy environment.\lCheck us out!

#org @gText_IcedPath_SwimmerFrancine_Before
I just swam in dirty, icy water\nto get here from Lavender Town[.]\lAnd I'd do it again, too!\lFufufu!

#org @gText_IcedPath_SwimmerFrancine_Lose
Swimming in dirty ice water is\nawesome and healthy. Try it!

