So you know, you can walk up and\ndown that rubble to get around!\pIt hurt my bare feet to walk on\njagged metal, but it's all okay!\pI'll just swim the pain off in the\nice pool.\pSomeone like YOU might need help\nfrom a Pok\emon to swim, though.\lCan't help you there.

#org @gText_IcedPath_SwimmerFrancine_VsSeeker
I'm feeling great after another icy\nswim! Gimme a rematch!

#org @gText_IcedPath_DiveHint
Icewater blocks the path below.\nIt looks deep enough to dive in[.]\lWith a Pok\emon's help, of course.\pOnly a fool would swim in that\nfrigid, dirty water without help!\pAs a matter of fact, there's a\nswimmer down there I came to stop.\pBut, my Psyduck doesn't know Surf.\pAnd swimming across myself would be\nhypocritical.